[I] KDE Frameworks addon with extra API to write KConfigModules

[T] Utilities for KDE System Settings modules. KCMUtils provides various
[T] classes to work with KCModules. KCModules can be created with the
[T] KConfigWidgets framework.

[U] https://www.kde.org

